            <div class="bottom">
                <h3>Beavers:</h3>
                <p>Say hello to our industrious beaver family, Chip and Willow, along with their adorable kits. These
                    remarkable rodents are known as nature's engineers, with their ability to build intricate dams and
                    lodges that play a vital role in maintaining healthy wetland ecosystems. Observe our beavers at work
                    as
                    they construct and maintain their impressive structures, using their sharp teeth and powerful tails.
                    Learn about their fascinating social behaviors, their importance in the ecosystem, and the
                    conservation
                    efforts in place to protect these incredible creatures.

                </p>
